\lim_{n \to \infty} \left(2\sqrt{n}\left(\sqrt{n+1}-\sqrt{n}\right)\right)^n
\frac{1}{e^{1/4}}
\lim_{n \to \infty} \left(2\sqrt{n}\times \frac{\left(\sqrt{n+1}-\sqrt{n}\right)\times \left(\sqrt{n+1}+\sqrt{n}\right)}{\left(\sqrt{n+1}+\sqrt{n}\right)}\right)^n=
\lim_{n \to \infty} \left(\frac{2\sqrt{n}}{\sqrt{n+1}+\sqrt{n}}\right)^n
\sqrt{1+x}
x=0
 \sqrt{1+x} = 1 + \frac{x}{2} - \frac{x^2}{8} + \mathcal{O}(x^3).
 \left( 2\sqrt{n} ( \sqrt{n+1} - \sqrt{n} )\right)^n =2^n n^{\frac{n+1}{2}} \left(\sqrt{1+\frac{1}{n}}-1 \right)^n
=2^n n^{\frac{n+1}{2}} \left( \frac{1}{2n} - \frac{1}{8n^2}+ \mathcal{O}(1/n^3)\right)^n = n^{\frac{1-n}{2}} \left(1 - \frac{1}{4n} + \mathcal{O}(n^{-2})\right)^n\to e^{-1/4}.
